{
  "text": "Eligibility criteria. Inclusion criteria for the case group (n = 12) were: a confirmed clinical DPN diagnosis with or without pain [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] and a Michigan Neuropathy Screening Instrument (MNSI) score \u22654",
